    <h1>Edge SEO</h1>
    <p class="description">Shipping technical SEO changes at the CDN layer — Cloudflare Workers, Fastly, Akamai — <strong>without dev-team involvement</strong>. Turns 6-week backlogs into 30-minute deploys.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
